From: Martin Schenk <martin.schenk@neukreativ.com>
Date: Sun, 28 Jun 2026 18:57:14 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Preserve style search when switching selector pills

Keep the Properties panel style search query when authors click
different selector pills on the same element, and auto-focus the
strongest matching pill that already sets a property for the query.

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
